{
  "design_notes": "The chart is designed for a Medium-level player, aligning note density with the per-bar energy levels of this 125 BPM track. It starts with solid quarter-note steps during the intro, scaling up to steady stream patterns with comfortable eighth-note sequences during the main drops. A generous number of holds are placed on major vocal and synth sustains, encouraging players to practice their weight-distribution and balance on the pad. The mid-section features a low-density breather with isolated taps to match the break, and the final drop drives energy home before a simple, satisfying taper on the outro.",
